# Verified Swing Pricing — Fusion Integration Prototype

A staged working prototype for the proposed JPM Fusion POC. One engine, three surfaces.

## What this proves

Synthetic data generation gets us reproducible Irish QIAIFs on demand. A Fusion-shaped semantic layer normalises the inputs. A neuro-symbolic calculation engine (LLM Builder + six verification layers) produces a swing factor that is provably correct, not just plausibly correct. Every certified output ships with its proof.

