## The engine (`verified_swing_pricing/core.py`)

Single module, ~300 lines, no heavy dependencies. All three surfaces import from here, so the demo cannot drift across surfaces.

- **Synthetic generator**: deterministic-from-seed Irish QIAIF. Controls: net flow %, asset mix, market regime.
- **Fusion-style Reader**: three upstream sources (Custody/FA/MO) in three formats, with persona-driven adversarial perturbations (header drift, unit drift, legacy-format collisions).
- **Semantic layer**: YAML-style entity definitions for Position, SubscriptionFlow, NAVStrike, SwingFactor — each with constraints, derivations, and Z3-checkable verification specs.
- **Swing-pricing calculation**: weighted transaction-cost model parameterised by liquidation horizon and stress.
- **Six-layer verification**: Z3 constitution, dual-Builder consensus, inverse verification, property-based testing, Tool Library regression, Anomaly Agent.
- **Signed certified output**: SHA-256 proof hash binds the output to its inputs.

